Quickstrike:





Quickstrike leaned against the mouth of the cave, glaring cooly at the bat. 
He looked left and right at the auto-guns at the cave, then to his two 
females. He leaned his shoulder against the rock formation. "Who ya wit' 
again?" he asked Battera.
